{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":744,"text":"I have the feeling that we can all agree"},{"time":3851,"text":"that we're moving towards a new"},{"time":6078,"text":"model of the state and society."},{"time":8943,"text":"But, we're absolutely clueless as to what this is"},{"time":13424,"text":"or what it should be."},{"time":15110,"text":"It seems like we need to have"},{"time":17137,"text":"a conversation about democracy"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20139,"text":"in our day and age."},{"time":22494,"text":"Let's think about it this way:"},{"time":24990,"text":"We are 21st-century citizens, doing our"},{"time":28976,"text":"very, very best to interact with 19th century-designed\ninstitutions"},{"time":35072,"text":"that are based on an information technology of the 15th century."},{"time":40395,"text":"Let's have a look at some of the"},{"time":41806,"text":"characteristics of this system."},{"time":44242,"text":"First of all, it's designed for an information technology"},{"time":47747,"text":"that's over 500 years old."},{"time":50846,"text":"And the best possible system"},{"time":53082,"text":"that could be designed for it"},{"time":54617,"text":"is one where the few make daily decisions"},{"time":58841,"text":"in the name of the many."},{"time":60275,"text":"And the many get to vote once every \ncouple of years."},{"time":65810,"text":"In the second place, the costs of"},{"time":67159,"text":"participating in this system are"},{"time":69451,"text":"incredibly high."},{"time":70658,"text":"You either have to have a fair \nbit of money"},{"time":73700,"text":"and influence, or you have to devote your entire"},{"time":78052,"text":"life to politics."},{"time":79890,"text":"You have to become a party member"},{"time":81830,"text":"and slowly start working up the ranks"},{"time":85448,"text":"until maybe, one day, you'll get \nto sit at a table"},{"time":89364,"text":"where a decision is being made."},{"time":91933,"text":"And last but not least,"},{"time":93749,"text":"the language of the system â€”"},{"time":95669,"text":"it's incredibly cryptic."},{"time":97518,"text":"It's done for lawyers, by lawyers,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":100702,"text":"and no one else can understand."},{"time":103548,"text":"So, it's a system where we can"},{"time":106223,"text":"choose our authorities,"},{"time":108158,"text":"but we are completely left out on how\nthose authorities"},{"time":111994,"text":"reach their decisions."},{"time":114845,"text":"So, in a day where a new information technology"},{"time":118160,"text":"allows us to participate globally\nin any conversation,"},{"time":124456,"text":"our barriers of information are completely lowered"},{"time":127609,"text":"and we can, more than ever before,"},{"time":131088,"text":"express our desires and our concerns."},{"time":134766,"text":"Our political system remains the same"},{"time":137519,"text":"for the past 200 years"},{"time":141135,"text":"and expects us to be contented with being \nsimply passive recipients"}]},{"cues":[{"time":146918,"text":"of a monologue."},{"time":148661,"text":"So, it's really not surprising that"},{"time":151104,"text":"this kind of system is only able to produce"},{"time":154446,"text":"two kinds of results:"},{"time":156378,"text":"silence or noise."},{"time":160047,"text":"Silence, in terms of citizens not engaging,"},{"time":163836,"text":"simply not wanting to participate."},{"time":166732,"text":"There's this commonplace \n[idea] that I truly, truly dislike,"},{"time":170010,"text":"and it's this idea that we citizens are naturally"},{"time":174069,"text":"apathetic. That we shun commitment."},{"time":177175,"text":"But, can you really blame us"},{"time":178702,"text":"for not jumping at the opportunity of going"},{"time":181576,"text":"to the middle of the city in the middle"},{"time":183595,"text":"of a working day to attend, physically,"},{"time":186944,"text":"a public hearing that has no impact"},{"time":190364,"text":"whatsoever?"},{"time":192304,"text":"Conflict is bound to happen between a system"},{"time":196692,"text":"that no longer represents, nor has any dialogue capacity,"},{"time":202887,"text":"and citizens that are increasingly used"},{"time":205965,"text":"to representing themselves."},{"time":208311,"text":"And, then we find noise:"},{"time":210615,"text":"Chile, Argentina, Brazil, Mexico\nItaly, France, Spain, the United States,"},{"time":216994,"text":"they're all democracies."},{"time":218853,"text":"Their citizens have access to"},{"time":220765,"text":"the ballot boxes. But they still feel the need,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":225021,"text":"they need to take to the streets in order \nto be heard."},{"time":230531,"text":"To me, it seems like the 18th-century"},{"time":235022,"text":"slogan that was the basis for the formation"},{"time":238082,"text":"of our modern democracies, \"No taxation"},{"time":241734,"text":"without representation,\""},{"time":244037,"text":"can now be updated to \"No representation\nwithout a conversation.\""},{"time":251168,"text":"We want our seat at the table."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255704,"text":"And rightly so."},{"time":258010,"text":"But in order to be part of this conversation,"},{"time":260390,"text":"we need to know what we want to do next,"},{"time":263901,"text":"because political action is being able"},{"time":267108,"text":"to move from agitation"},{"time":269429,"text":"to construction."},{"time":271293,"text":"My generation has been incredibly good at"},{"time":275130,"text":"using new networks and technologies"},{"time":277751,"text":"to organize protests,"},{"time":280266,"text":"protests that were able to successfully"},{"time":282684,"text":"impose agendas,"},{"time":284643,"text":"roll back extremely pernicious legislation,"},{"time":288066,"text":"and even overthrow authoritarian governments."},{"time":291267,"text":"And we should be immensely"},{"time":293263,"text":"proud of this."},{"time":295622,"text":"But, we also must admit that we"},{"time":297470,"text":"haven't been good at using those"},{"time":299958,"text":"same networks and technologies"},{"time":302846,"text":"to successfully articulate an alternative\nto what we're seeing"},{"time":308244,"text":"and find the consensus and build \nthe alliances that are needed"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313061,"text":"to make it happen."},{"time":315079,"text":"And so the risk that we face"},{"time":317575,"text":"is that we can create these huge power vacuums"},{"time":321208,"text":"that will very quickly get filled up by de facto"},{"time":325295,"text":"powers, like the military or highly"},{"time":328176,"text":"motivated and already organized groups"}]},{"cues":[{"time":331075,"text":"that generally lie on the extremes."},{"time":334745,"text":"But our democracy is neither"},{"time":336697,"text":"just a matter of voting once every"},{"time":339466,"text":"couple of years."},{"time":340721,"text":"But it's not either the ability to bring millions\nonto the streets."},{"time":346657,"text":"So the question I'd like to raise here,"},{"time":349478,"text":"and I do believe it's the most important \nquestion we need to answer,"},{"time":353000,"text":"is this one:"},{"time":354357,"text":"If Internet is the new printing press,"},{"time":358036,"text":"then what is democracy for the Internet era?"},{"time":362872,"text":"What institutions do we want to build"}]},{"cues":[{"time":365822,"text":"for the 21st-century society?"},{"time":369781,"text":"I don't have the answer, just in case."},{"time":373007,"text":"I don't think anyone does."},{"time":374441,"text":"But I truly believe we can't afford\nto ignore this question anymore."},{"time":379456,"text":"So, I'd like to share our experience"},{"time":381393,"text":"and what we've learned so far"},{"time":383119,"text":"and hopefully contribute two cents"}]},{"cues":[{"time":385542,"text":"to this conversation."},{"time":387720,"text":"Two years ago, with a group of friends\nfrom Argentina,"},{"time":391438,"text":"we started thinking, \"how can \nwe get our representatives,"},{"time":395487,"text":"our elected representatives,"},{"time":397371,"text":"to represent us?\""},{"time":401719,"text":"Marshall McLuhan once said that politics"},{"time":405724,"text":"is solving today's problems with yesterday's tools."},{"time":410419,"text":"So the question that motivated us was,"},{"time":412933,"text":"can we try and solve some of today's problems"},{"time":416827,"text":"with the tools that we use every single\nday of our lives?"},{"time":420929,"text":"Our first approach was to design and develop"},{"time":423879,"text":"a piece of software called DemocracyOS."},{"time":427130,"text":"DemocracyOS is an open-source web application"},{"time":430255,"text":"that is designed to become a bridge"},{"time":433453,"text":"between citizens and their elected representatives"}]},{"cues":[{"time":436531,"text":"to make it easier for us to participate \nfrom our everyday lives."},{"time":442239,"text":"So first of all, you can get informed so every new"},{"time":445578,"text":"project that gets introduced in Congress"},{"time":448254,"text":"gets immediately translated and explained"},{"time":451383,"text":"in plain language on this platform."},{"time":454318,"text":"But we all know that social change"},{"time":457614,"text":"is not going to come from just knowing"},{"time":460372,"text":"more information,"},{"time":461644,"text":"but from doing something with it."},{"time":464143,"text":"So better access to information"},{"time":466362,"text":"should lead to a conversation"},{"time":468693,"text":"about what we're going to do next,"},{"time":470544,"text":"and DemocracyOS allows for that."},{"time":472626,"text":"Because we believe that democracy is"},{"time":474912,"text":"not just a matter of stacking up"},{"time":476957,"text":"preferences, one on top of each other,"},{"time":479776,"text":"but that our healthy and robust public debate"}]},{"cues":[{"time":483484,"text":"should be, once again, one of its fundamental values."},{"time":487541,"text":"So DemocracyOS is about persuading \nand being persuaded."},{"time":491743,"text":"It's about reaching a consensus"},{"time":494474,"text":"as much as finding a proper way"},{"time":497771,"text":"of channeling our disagreement."},{"time":500496,"text":"And finally, you can vote"},{"time":502486,"text":"how you would like your elected \nrepresentative to vote."},{"time":506586,"text":"And if you do not feel comfortable"},{"time":508026,"text":"voting on a certain issue,"},{"time":510140,"text":"you can always delegate your vote"},{"time":512024,"text":"to someone else, allowing"}]},{"cues":[{"time":513767,"text":"for a dynamic and emerging social leadership."},{"time":519346,"text":"It suddenly became very easy for us"},{"time":520729,"text":"to simply compare these results"},{"time":523444,"text":"with how our representatives were"},{"time":525148,"text":"voting in Congress."},{"time":526551,"text":"But, it also became very evident that"},{"time":528984,"text":"technology was not going to do the trick."},{"time":532942,"text":"What we needed to do to was to find"},{"time":534821,"text":"actors that were able to"},{"time":537441,"text":"grab this distributed knowledge"},{"time":540345,"text":"in society and use it to make better\nand more fair decisions."},{"time":546409,"text":"So we reached out to traditional political parties"},{"time":549697,"text":"and we offered them DemocracyOS."},{"time":551892,"text":"We said, \"Look, here you have a platform\nthat you can use to build"},{"time":556216,"text":"a two-way conversation with your constituencies.\""},{"time":560124,"text":"And yes, we failed."},{"time":562687,"text":"We failed big time."},{"time":565683,"text":"We were sent to play \noutside like little kids."},{"time":570009,"text":"Amongst other things, we were called naive."},{"time":572405,"text":"And I must be honest: I think, in hindsight, we were."},{"time":576201,"text":"Because the challenges that we face, they're not"},{"time":578667,"text":"technological, they're cultural."},{"time":581552,"text":"Political parties were never willing"},{"time":583946,"text":"to change the way they make their decisions."},{"time":587950,"text":"So it suddenly became a bit obvious"},{"time":589678,"text":"that if we wanted to move forward\nwith this idea,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":593094,"text":"we needed to do it ourselves."},{"time":596035,"text":"And so we took quite a leap of faith,"},{"time":598044,"text":"and in August last year, we founded"},{"time":600869,"text":"our own political party,"},{"time":602965,"text":"El Partido de la Red,"},{"time":604078,"text":"or the Net Party, in the city of \nBuenos Aires."},{"time":608250,"text":"And taking an even bigger leap of faith,"},{"time":611927,"text":"we ran for elections in October last year"},{"time":616173,"text":"with this idea:"},{"time":617769,"text":"if we want a seat in Congress,"},{"time":620366,"text":"our candidate, our representatives"},{"time":622384,"text":"were always going to vote according to"},{"time":625758,"text":"what citizens decided on DemocracyOS."},{"time":629267,"text":"Every single project that got introduced"},{"time":632119,"text":"in Congress, we were going vote"},{"time":633846,"text":"according to what citizens decided\non an online platform."},{"time":638588,"text":"It was our way of hacking the political system."},{"time":642238,"text":"We understood that if we wanted"},{"time":644164,"text":"to become part of the conversation,"},{"time":646513,"text":"to have a seat at the table,"},{"time":648185,"text":"we needed to become valid stakeholders,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":651894,"text":"and the only way of doing it is to play by the \nsystem rules."},{"time":656116,"text":"But we were hacking it in the sense that"},{"time":659105,"text":"we were radically changing the way a political party"},{"time":663193,"text":"makes its decisions."},{"time":664612,"text":"For the first time, we were making our decisions"},{"time":668115,"text":"together with those who we were"}]},{"cues":[{"time":670868,"text":"affecting directly by those decisions."},{"time":675247,"text":"It was a very, very bold move for a two-month-old party"},{"time":678985,"text":"in the city of Buenos Aires."},{"time":680664,"text":"But it got attention."},{"time":682239,"text":"We got 22,000 votes, that's 1.2 percent of the votes,"},{"time":686952,"text":"and we came in second for the local options."},{"time":691128,"text":"So, even if that wasn't enough to win a"},{"time":693328,"text":"seat in Congress, it was enough"},{"time":695454,"text":"for us to become part of the conversation,"},{"time":698637,"text":"to the extent that next month,"},{"time":702208,"text":"Congress, as an institution, is launching"},{"time":705229,"text":"for the first time in Argentina's history,"},{"time":708097,"text":"a DemocracyOS to discuss,"},{"time":710519,"text":"with the citizens, three pieces of legislation:"},{"time":714189,"text":"two on urban transportation and"}]},{"cues":[{"time":716296,"text":"one on the use of public space."},{"time":719288,"text":"Of course, our elected representatives are not"},{"time":722077,"text":"saying, \"Yes, we're going to vote"},{"time":724094,"text":"according to what citizens decide,\""},{"time":726667,"text":"but they're willing to try."},{"time":728693,"text":"They're willing to open up a new space"},{"time":731923,"text":"for citizen engagement and hopefully"}]},{"cues":[{"time":734568,"text":"they'll be willing to listen as well."},{"time":737824,"text":"Our political system can be transformed,"},{"time":741888,"text":"and not by subverting it, by destroying it,"},{"time":745566,"text":"but by rewiring it with the tools that"}]},{"cues":[{"time":749185,"text":"Internet affords us now."},{"time":751937,"text":"But a real challenge is to find, to design"},{"time":756324,"text":"to create, to empower those connectors"},{"time":759753,"text":"that are able to innovate, to transform"},{"time":763572,"text":"noise and silence into signal"},{"time":766240,"text":"and finally bring our democracies"}]},{"cues":[{"time":768178,"text":"to the 21st century."},{"time":770506,"text":"I'm not saying it's easy."},{"time":773237,"text":"But in our experience, we actually stand a chance"},{"time":776820,"text":"of making it work."},{"time":779154,"text":"And in my heart, it's most definitely"},{"time":782286,"text":"worth trying."},{"time":783567,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":784799,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}